During the meeting, we discussed a plan to expedite the implementation of the objectives of the 2021 National Agenda, and we approved the formation of 36 specialized teams of 550 government officials for implementation
The national agenda includes 52 specific goals in the sectors of education, health, housing, society, infrastructure, economy, environment, security, justice and safety

The national agenda summarizes the work of the government and shortens the goals that we set for the happiness of our people. The focus on the coming period will be the priority and the goal of government action
At the meeting, we were given the full authority of the team to use any staff member in any federal agency to join the national agenda team, the remaining 5 years to achieve all the goals.
The government has made huge achievements, big leaps and global centers over the past years, but we want all its members to act as quickly
During the meeting, we also discussed the consolidated financial statements of the State and adopted the final accounts of a group of federal entities
We have also adopted a comprehensive agreement with the United States for cooperation in the field of air navigation, exploration and use of airspace and outer space for peaceful purposes
